       int aIn_RS,
       int aIn_RT,
       int aIn_Immediate)
        This operation adds either two registers or one register and an immediate operator.
        Parameters:
        aIn_RD - The location to put the result.
        aIn_RS - One value to be added.
        aIn_RT - The other value to be added.
        aIn_Immediate - The other value to be added.

      • getPostALUDestReg

        int getPostALUDestReg(boolean clear)
        Get the destination register for the op result from the post ALU access buffer and possibly clears the buffer.
        Parameters:
        clear - True if the buffer will be cleared, false if the buffer will stay.
        Returns:

      • getPostALUDestReg2

        Returns:
